headline.main: After Outcry, Israeli Arab Town Removes Sign Honoring Arafat
headline.print_headline: After Outcry, Israeli Arab Town Removes Sign Honoring Arafat

lead_paragraph: Israel's interior ministry says an Arab town that named a street after the late Palestinian leader Yasser Arafat has removed the sign bearing his name.
